'''Breil''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] located on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. This settlement was known for its size, and the word ''breil'' was often used as a Bothan family name. [[Tav Breil'lya]], aide to [[Borsk Fey'lya]], was a noted user of this prefix.

